abstract: Romanian officials report two more people haved died from injuries sustained in October fire in Bucharest nightclub, raising death toll from blaze to 53.
lead_paragraph: Two more people have died of burns sustained in a nightclub fire last month in Bucharest, officials said.

headline.print_headline: Europe; Romania: Fire’s Death Toll Increases
